<br>
For the third time tonight Apollo cleared his voice and a thick silence fell upon the room.<br>
<br>
&quot;I suggest we start this &quot;final judgement&quot; of sorts. Everyone move away from Paris, we don't want anyone, but the three goddesses to manipulate his vote.&quot; Apollo smirked.<br>
<br>
