&quot;Let's get this party started!&quot; he almost hollared as he danced back to his seat. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 221<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/21/01 3:45:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=151>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gaurentee of a Speedy Trial</span><hr size=1> ::Poseidon looked to Apollo as he seemed a bit hasty of getting things started. He walked to a table full of food and drink of different kinds and picked up a goblet and poured himself some wine. Then he strode over to Apollo pulled out a chair and took a seat by the Sun God. He stretched his legs out and folded his ankles over each other and sips at the contents of his goblet. He stares at the goddesses at first and then looks over at Apollo with a smile on his red stained lips.::<br>
