::She tosses back in forth the chance of a lifetime to Paris in her head.  Should she offer the most beautiful mortal to him?  She saves this &quot;ace of spade&quot; to see what Athena has up her toga sleeve.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=goddessathena>Goddess Athena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/22/01 1:24:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=154>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Wisdom and War</span><hr size=1> Athena grinned at the mortal man already seeing Hera and Aphrodite go into action with bribes. Or at least, thinking of them.<br>
<br>
Athena stood there in her golden glory with her hands upon her hips. She was truly the highest in virtue and power.<br>
<br>
She rolled her eyes at Poseidon and Apollo, the both of them already on her badside. She wanted to be fair about the judgement that young Paris had to make, and being fair would mean that she would too bribe him as well.<br>
<br>
She smiled making her way over to him speaking.<br>
<br>
&quot;I know you shall make a wise decision Paris, for your own good naturally.&quot;<br>
<br>
Her voice was then cloaked and the only one with enough power to hear her would have been Zeus himself, as she spoke to Paris and ONLY Paris.<br>
<br>
&quot;Imagine comming home from battle as the Greatest warrior in the world. With the most strength and skill any man or ~*~woman~*~ has ever seen.&quot;<br>
<br>
She grinned lightly.<br>
<br>
&quot;You're a warrior at heart Paris, and you'd love to be the greatest.&quot;<br>
<br>
She could already feel him wanting her words.<br>
<br>
&quot;Choose me, and you'll be greater than Heracles. More famous than any mortal ever to step foot on the Earth.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
