<br>
His eyes wandered to those of the fair eyed Paris. He saw the grin smear its way onto his face.<br>
Athena had surely bribed him with something trivial, like victory in battle, or endless knowledge. Did she not realize that Paris was a country bumpkin at heart? This was one of the first social gatherings (upper-class social gatherings) he's ever been too. And Athena was promising him things that in the long run, he wouldn't care for. If it had been up to Apollo, and he had been offered the two...he'd of picked Hera's...but what ever.<br>
<br>
Apollo waited for Aphrodite's bribe. Surely she would offer him something of substance, something the young country hick would actually want. Something he could fathom actually attaining. A woman perhaps....<br>
<br>
Apollo juggled the thought as he sipped his wine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unikeqofv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NikeQofV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 111<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/22/01 9:17:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=156>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~dave.newton/lysette-anthony/pictures/lysette-anthony109.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Choosing a Winner</span><hr size=1> ::Nike looks over the entire event, keeping completly silent knowing she played a key role in determining the winner. Shakes her head knowin that Paris will get punished no matter whom he chooses. Shrugs as she contemplates, had to be someone. She listens carefully as Hera gives hroffer to him. Nah, not good enough really. She looks over to Aphrodite. She'll definitely offer a woman, probably a married one. The married women are always the most desirable for some reason. Besides, she doesn't really have anything else to offer because Paris is already handsome. <br>
