::Nike turns her head towards Athena sharp and quickly as her bribing words trickle into her ears, despite th talkings of the room. Was Athena offering Paris victory? She listens as Athena finishes her bribe and steps away from paris. She was, she actully offered Paris glory, victory, and success. Nike crosses her arms and a small knowing smirk touches her lips. Athena was about to learn a little lesson today, which Nike would explain to her later ::<br>
