<br>
Now, knowing Nike well enough to tell that she was not about to be used, he could conclude that the game was up for Athena. Nike would refuse to grant Paris the &quot;victory&quot; that Athena so ignorantly promised to Paris. <br>
<br>
&quot;Ahahaha, sweet irony.&quot; Apollo muttered as he shook the hair from his eyes. Athena's &quot;Sure to win&quot; bribe was the very promise that was to make her &quot;Sure to lose&quot;. Apollo shook with the chuckles.<br>
<br>
&quot;Foolishness.&quot; Those were the words that escaped Apollo's lips as he shook his head. Athena had just outted herself from this little competition without knowing a thing of it. Nike would not grant Athena victory on this day. Everything was falling into place. Aphrodite was the only one left to bribe Paris, and if she didn't flub it up, she was almost sure to win. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/23/01 9:10:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=158>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.xenafan.com/gallery/if_the_shoe_fits/itsf254aphrodite27.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Getting out the big guns</span><hr size=1> ::Aphrodite slowly and gracefully walks over to Paris and rests both her hands on his right should.  She gently rest her head on her hands, which strategically postions her mouth within centimeters of Paris' ear.::<br>
<br>
::  She whispers soflty and coolly::<br>
